26#ifndef _I915_GEM_RENDER_STATE_H_
27#define _I915_GEM_RENDER_STATE_H_
28
29#include <linux/types.h>
30
31struct intel_renderstate_rodata {
32 const u32 *reloc;
33 const u32 *batch;
34 const u32 batch_items;
35};
36
37struct render_state {
38 const struct intel_renderstate_rodata *rodata;
39 struct drm_i915_gem_object *obj;
40 u64 ggtt_offset;
41 int gen;
42 u32 aux_batch_size;
43 u32 aux_batch_offset;
44};
45
46int i915_gem_render_state_init(struct drm_i915_gem_request *req);
47void i915_gem_render_state_fini(struct render_state *so);
48int i915_gem_render_state_prepare(struct intel_engine_cs *ring,
49 struct render_state *so);
50
51#endif /* _I915_GEM_RENDER_STATE_H_ */
